#: ../../content/applications/productivity/discuss/overview/plan_activities.rst-1
msgid ""
"View of an activity type form emphasizing the field recommended next activities for Odoo\n"
"Discuss"
msgstr "DOdoo讨论应用中强调推荐后续活动的字段的活动类型表单视图"

