"要更改上传图片的显示大小，在:guilable:`尺寸`选项下选择:guilabel:`小`、:guilale:`中`或:guilalb:`大`。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/studio/fields.rst:303
msgid "Sign (`binary`)"
